result.name: hs2-phase-two-from-the-west-midlands-to-leeds-and-manchester
result.notes:
HS2 Phase 2b: from the West Midlands to Leeds and Crewe to Manchester

The data provided here relates to information and/or engineering design published during the Development Phase of High Speed Two (HS2) Phase 2b, and described within the High Speed Rail (Crewe to Manchester) Environmental Statement deposited in Parliament as part of the hybrid Bill deposit in January 2022. Accessing the data in these formats may require specialised equipment, programmes or products. The data does not form part of the ES. It is not necessary to be able to access or view the information in these formats in order to participate in any active consultations.

organization.name: high-speed-2
organization.title: High Speed 2 Limited
organization.description:
High Speed Two Limited (HS2 Ltd) is responsible for developing proposals for a new national high speed rail network. It is a company limited by guarantee and wholly funded by grant-in-aid from the government.

HS2 is an executive non-departmental public body of the Department for Transport

http://www.hs2.org.uk/
